      • create

        public static Extent create(double xmin,
            double ymin,
            double xmax,
            double ymax,
            SpatialReference ref)
        Creates a new Extent object. The coordinates represent the lower left and upper right corners of the bounding box. A spatial reference is also required.
        Parameters:
        xmin - - Bottom-left X-coordinate of an extent envelope.
        ymin - - Bottom-left Y-coordinate of an extent envelope.
        xmax - - Top-right X-coordinate of an extent envelope.
        ymax - - Top-right Y-coordinate of an extent envelope.
        ref - - Spatial reference of the geometry.
        Returns:
        Extent
